      "title": "Blog progress",
      "description": "",
      "content": "<h2 id=\"背景\">\n<span class=\"me-2\">背景</span><a href=\"#%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF\" class=\"anchor text-muted\"><i class=\"fas fa-hashtag\"></i></a>\n</h2>\n\n<p>这个Blog 使用<a href=\"https://jekyllrb.com\">Jekyll blog</a> 搭建, 服务使用 Github.io 来做的, 跑了大概半年后，现在想给它加入 tag 功能，主要后面做下区分，也方便去做索引处理。</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"加入tags-功能\">\n<span class=\"me-2\">加入tags 功能</span><a href=\"#%E5%8A%A0%E5%85%A5tags-%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD\" class=\"anchor text-muted\"><i class=\"fas fa-hashtag\"></i></a>\n</h2>\n\n<p>这里加入Tag 的操作，增加Plug 模块，打开 _config.yml，找到plug并在下面加入 - jekyll-archives - jekyll-sitemap 两个模块。</p>\n\n<p>然后就是在_posts 目录下面的每个文件中，加入categories 和 tags 即可，多个使用空格分割。</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"post-格式\">\n<span class=\"me-2\">Post 格式</span><a href=\"#post-%E6%A0%BC%E5%BC%8F\" class=\"anchor text-muted\"><i class=\"fas fa-hashtag\"></i></a>\n</h2>\n\n<h3 id=\"代码\">\n<span class=\"me-2\">代码</span><a href=\"#%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81\" class=\"anchor text-muted\"><i class=\"fas fa-hashtag\"></i></a>\n</h3>\n\n<p>注意点:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>首字母小写</li>\n  <li>\n    <p><code>Objective-c</code> need replace to <code>objc</code> for code syntax.</p>\n  </li>\n  <li>常用一些 <code>Crash</code>, <code>堆栈信息</code>, 这类都统一使用<code>console</code> 即可.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<blockquote>\n  <p><sup id=\"fnref:write-a-new-post\"><a href=\"#fn:write-a-new-post\" class=\"footnote\" rel=\"footnote\" role=\"doc-noteref\">1</a></sup> By default, all languages except plaintext, console, and terminal will display line numbers. When you want to hide the line number of a code block, add the class nolineno to it:</p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<div class=\"language-markdown highlighter-rouge\">\n<div class=\"code-header\">\n<span data-label-text=\"Markdown\"><i class=\"fas fa-code fa-fw small\"></i></span><button aria-label=\"copy\" data-title-succeed=\"Copied!\"><i class=\"far fa-clipboard\"></i></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><code><table class=\"rouge-table\"><tbody><tr>\n<td class=\"rouge-gutter gl\"><pre class=\"lineno\">1\n2\n3\n4\n</pre></td>\n<td class=\"rouge-code\"><pre><span class=\"p\">```</span><span class=\"nl\">shell\n</span><span class=\"nb\">echo</span> <span class=\"s1\">'No more line numbers!'</span>\n<span class=\"p\">```</span>\n{: .nolineno }\n</pre></td>\n</tr></tbody></table></code></div>\n</div>\n\n<p>更多<sup id=\"fnref:code-table\"><a href=\"#fn:code-table\" class=\"footnote\" rel=\"footnote\" role=\"doc-noteref\">2</a></sup>.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"reverse-footnote\">\n<span class=\"me-2\">Reverse Footnote</span><a href=\"#reverse-footnote\" class=\"anchor text-muted\"><i class=\"fas fa-hashtag\"></i></a>\n</h2>\n\n<div class=\"footnotes\" role=\"doc-endnotes\">\n  <ol>\n    <li id=\"fn:write-a-new-post\">\n      <p><a href=\"https://chirpy.cotes.page/posts/write-a-new-post/\">write-a-new-post</a> <a href=\"#fnref:write-a-new-post\" class=\"reversefootnote\" role=\"doc-backlink\">↩</a></p>\n    </li>\n    <li id=\"fn:code-table\">\n      <p><a href=\"https://www.fabriziomusacchio.com/blog/2021-08-11-Syntax_Highlighting_in_Jekyll/\">Supported syntax highlighting in Jekyll</a> <a href=\"#fnref:code-table\" class=\"reversefootnote\" role=\"doc-backlink\">↩</a></p>\n    </li>\n  </ol>\n</div>\n"
    },
    "en": {
      "title": "Blog progress",
      "description": "",
      "content": "<h2 id=\"背景\">\n<span class=\"me-2\">background</span><a href=\"#%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF\" class=\"anchor text-muted\"><i class=\"fas fa-hashtag\"></i></a>\n</h2>\n\n<p>This blog uses<a href=\"https://jekyllrb.com\">Jekyll blog</a>The service was built using Github.io and has been running for about six months. Now we want to add a tag feature to it, mainly to differentiate between different services and to make indexing easier.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"加入tags-功能\">\n<span class=\"me-2\">Add tags feature</span><a href=\"#%E5%8A%A0%E5%85%A5tags-%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD\" class=\"anchor text-muted\"><i class=\"fas fa-hashtag\"></i></a>\n</h2>\n\n<p>To add tags, add the Plug module. Open _config.yml, find plug, and add the two modules - jekyll-archives - jekyll-sitemap below it.</p>\n\n<p>Then, in each file under the _posts directory, add categories and tags, separating multiple categories with spaces.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"post-格式\">\n<span class=\"me-2\">Post format</span><a href=\"#post-%E6%A0%BC%E5%BC%8F\" class=\"anchor text-muted\"><i class=\"fas fa-hashtag\"></i></a>\n</h2>\n\n<h3 id=\"代码\">\n<span class=\"me-2\">code</span><a href=\"#%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81\" class=\"anchor text-muted\"><i class=\"fas fa-hashtag\"></i></a>\n</h3>\n\n<p>Points to note:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>Lowercase first letter</li>\n  <li>\n    <p><code>Objective-c</code> need replace to <code>objc</code> for code syntax.</p>\n  </li>\n  <li>Commonly used<code>Crash</code>, <code>堆栈信息</code>These types all use the same standard.<code>console</code>That's all.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<blockquote>\n  <p><sup id=\"fnref:write-a-new-post\"><a href=\"#fn:write-a-new-post\" class=\"footnote\" rel=\"footnote\" role=\"doc-noteref\">1</a></sup> By default, all languages except plaintext, console, and terminal will display line numbers. When you want to hide the line number of a code block, add the class nolineno to it:</p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<div class=\"language-markdown highlighter-rouge\">\n<div class=\"code-header\">\n<span data-label-text=\"Markdown\"><i class=\"fas fa-code fa-fw small\"></i></span><button aria-label=\"copy\" data-title-succeed=\"Copied!\"><i class=\"far fa-clipboard\"></i></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><code><table class=\"rouge-table\"><tbody><tr>\n<td class=\"rouge-gutter gl\"><pre class=\"lineno\">1\n2\n3\n4\n</pre></td>\n<td class=\"rouge-code\"><pre><span class=\"p\">```</span><span class=\"nl\">shell\n</span><span class=\"nb\">echo</span> <span class=\"s1\">'No more line numbers!'</span>\n<span class=\"p\">```</span>\n{: .nolineno }\n</pre></td>\n</tr></tbody></table></code></div>\n</div>\n\n<p>More<sup id=\"fnref:code-table\"><a href=\"#fn:code-table\" class=\"footnote\" rel=\"footnote\" role=\"doc-noteref\">2</a></sup>.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"reverse-footnote\">\n<span class=\"me-2\">Reverse Footnote</span><a href=\"#reverse-footnote\" class=\"anchor text-muted\"><i class=\"fas fa-hashtag\"></i></a>\n</h2>\n\n<div class=\"footnotes\" role=\"doc-endnotes\">\n  <ol>\n    <li id=\"fn:write-a-new-post\">\n      <p><a href=\"https://chirpy.cotes.page/posts/write-a-new-post/\">write-a-new-post</a> <a href=\"#fnref:write-a-new-post\" class=\"reversefootnote\" role=\"doc-backlink\">↩</a></p>\n    </li>\n    <li id=\"fn:code-table\">\n      <p><a href=\"https://www.fabriziomusacchio.com/blog/2021-08-11-Syntax_Highlighting_in_Jekyll/\">Supported syntax highlighting in Jekyll</a> <a href=\"#fnref:code-table\" class=\"reversefootnote\" role=\"doc-backlink\">↩</a></p>\n    </li>\n  </ol>\n</div>\n"
    }
